OL,3,C"That's my boy": 100-year-old reunites
OL,4,Cwith spitfire she built for World War
OL,5,CTwo
OL,7,FA 100-year-old wartime factory worker
OL,8,Fhas been reunited with the spitfire
OL,9,Fplane that she helped build.
OL,11,FMegan Langdell, 100, is one of the few
OL,12,Fwomen still alive who helped build
OL,13,Fspitfires during World War Two. Before
OL,14,Fthe war she crafted chairs and bus
OL,15,Fseats.
OL,17,FThe 100-year-old visited the Dumfries
OL,18,Fand Galloway Aviation Museum to see
OL,19,Fthe aeroplane on display, which was
OL,20,Frestored in 2017.
