OL,4,Cwith spitfire she built for World War
OL,5,CTwo
OL,7,FMegan said: "I was nine years in one
OL,8,Ffirm where they did the exhausts.
OL,10,F"We had two parts of metal for the
OL,11,Fexhaust and we had to self-weld
OL,12,Ftogether - and we had to get it
OL,13,Fperfect because it was someone's life.
OL,15,FMklla was the name of the spitfire
OL,16,FMegan helped create. The aeroplane was
OL,17,Flost in a training accident in Loch
OL,18,FDoon, East Ayrshire, on 25 October
OL,19,F1941.
