OL,7,FShe said: "I'm passionate about it, I
OL,8,Falways have been.
OL,10,F"They have a show every year in Moffat
OL,11,Fand the planes go over, and then the
OL,12,Fspitfires go over, I always say
OL,13,F'that's my boy'."
OL,15,FReminiscing on her time in the
OL,16,Ffactory, Megan added: "Where I worked
OL,17,Fwas a huge factory.
